Yawan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma a Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020
Cunkoson kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) na nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma a Burtaniya, wanda ke tabbatar da cewa, duk da cewa a wani mataki daban dangane da ƙasa, annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a kowace ƙasa.
Dangane da kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da UTIs dole ne su shirya sosai don barkewar marasa lafiya da COVID-19 waɗanda zasu buƙaci kulawa da kuma musamman kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an ba da rahoton wani kaso na cutar huhu da ba a san asalinsa ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Sin ta sanar da mai haifar da cutar a matsayin sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus, wanda yanzu ake kira da cutar coronavirus 2 na cutar mai saurin numfashi (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 ana kiranta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaida ta zuwa yanzu ita ce kashi 80 cikin 100 na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna samun nau'in cutar mai saurin kamuwa, wato, kamuwa da cuta ta numfashi tare da ko ba tare da ciwon huhu ba, kuma yawancin su suna murmurewa.
A kusan kashi 14 cikin dari na cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba zuwa mummunar cuta, tana bukatar a kwantar da ita a asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin dari na sauran cutar ke ci gaba zuwa mummunar cuta, tana bukatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin dari.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da kuma a Burtaniya kuma mun gwada su da lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
Mun kuma gwada adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a yanzu a ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya da na Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu da 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Al'ummar EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun kamu da cutar COVID-19
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya bazu a geographical, kuma yanayin annobar COVID-19 a sauran duniya a halin yanzu yana bin wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, darakta janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai, bisa ga ma'anar yanayin WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, an ba da rahoton farkon mutane uku da aka tabbatar da su a Faransa a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020 a cikin mutanen da ke dawowa daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an riga an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da kuma a Burtaniya, kuma tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da kwanan wata da aka ambata a sama, an samu rahoton kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 tare da kamuwa da cutar 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun adadi da yawan adadin cutar COVID-19
A Cibiyar Kare da Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), ana sabunta adadin mutanen da aka ba da rahoton COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda aka samo ne kawai daga tushen hukuma, kamar ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki, da WHO, kowace rana da karfe 8 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a EU/EEA da United Kingdom, da kuma kwatanta su da na Italiya.
A matsayin kusanci na yaduwar masu cutar COVID-19, mun kiyasta adadin adadin kwanaki 14 na COVID-19, saboda haka muna la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin mutanen da aka sanar da su a kowace kasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8 na safe, kuma mun kwatanta da na Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Yanayin a cikin kwanaki 14 na yawan cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da kuma Birtaniya gabaɗaya ya bi na lardin Hubei na kasar Sin (Hoto 1).
Gabaɗaya, ga EU/EEA da United Kingdom, adadin cutar COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu kuma ya ƙaru sosai a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (abubuwan da aka kara).
Wannan ya faru ne musamman saboda saurin karuwar al'amuran da aka ruwaito a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan yanayin karuwa a yawan cutar COVID-19 (kayan aiki).
Hoto 2 ya nuna adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da United Kingdom idan aka kwatanta da Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Ya ce a ranar 15 ga watan Maris, 15 sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Birtaniya sun riga sun ba da rahoton adadin masu kamuwa da cutar da ya yi daidai da na Italiya makonni uku da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin waɗanda aka ba da rahoton COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya.
Yanayin da aka lura da shi a cikin tarin cutar COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba a irin wannan saurin a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan duk da cewa ƙasashe suna cikin matakai daban-daban, bambancin ayyukan tsarin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa, da kuma yiwuwar ma'anar shari'o'i daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe da kuma ka'idoji daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya waɗanda za a gwada don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwaji don sabuntawa.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya sun bayyana halin da 10% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ruwaito cewa asibitoci da sassan kulawa mai tsanani a wadannan yankuna sun kai ga iyakar karfin su.
Bayanai kan shigar da mutane asibiti da kuma/ko kuma a cibiyar kula da marasa lafiya da cutar COVID-19 a halin yanzu suna samuwa a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'i, bi da bi (bayanai ba a nuna su ba).
Duk da haka, ya kamata a tattara su a hanya mai tsari don ƙara yawan bayanan sa ido na yanzu da ke mai da hankali kan adadin waɗanda aka ba da rahoto da kuma adadin waɗanda suka mutu.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar tsakanin 2010 zuwa 2011 ya nuna cewa akwai bambanci sosai a samuwar gadajen IUD da na sashin kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, daga gadaje 29,2 a Jamus zuwa gadaje 4.2 a Portugal a kan mutane 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun ƙarin ko ƙasa da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 gadajen ICU da na magani mai saurin-sauri don yawan mutane 100,000 a tsakanin 2010 da 2011).
An samar da yanayin da aka tsara dangane da yawan iyawar tsarin kiwon lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya na yawan masu shiga asibiti saboda COVID-19 da ke da haɗarin sama da kashi 90% na iyawar gadajen kulawa mai tsanani a cikin sabuntawa ta shida na ECDC na saurin kimanta hadarin COVID-19.
Tun da yake har zuwa yanzu an mayar da hankali kan wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da kuma United Kingdom, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin jinya na gaggawa suna kula da wani yanki da aka tsara, ya kamata a samar da bayanai kan shari'o'i da kuma gadajen jinya a cikin Nomenclature na Ƙungiyoyin Ƙasa don Ƙididdigar 2 (NUTS-2).
Misalin Italiya da kuma yanayin da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe ya nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba cikin sauri a EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, ya kamata kasashe, asibitoci da kuma UTI su shirya don yanayin watsa SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma karuwar adadin marasa lafiya da ke dauke da COVID-19 da ke bukatar kulawa ta likita, musamman kulawa mai tsanani, kamar yadda ake yi a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka jaddada a cikin saurin kimanta hadarin ECDC, hanzari, da kuma cikakkiyar hanya na da mahimmanci wajen jinkirta yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, tare da sauya daga tsarin kamewa zuwa tsarin ragewa, tunda saurin karuwar da ake tsammani a yawan shari'o'in na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, yarda da daidaita ayyukansu yadda ya kamata, idan ba a aiwatar da su ba a gaba.
Binciken gaggawa na hadarin ya kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a don rage tasirin annobar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokacin da ƙasashe za su iya ƙara matakan sarrafa cutar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma rage matsin lamba a kan tsarin kiwon lafiya.
Idan suka kasa yin haka, tsarin kiwon lafiya na wasu ƙasashen EU/EEA na iya samun ƙaruwar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
