An san cewa hawan cytokine yana zuwa ne daga tsananin halayen tsarin garkuwar jiki a cikin marasa lafiya da ke da cutar SARS da MERS.
Cytokine cascade wani nau'i ne na amsawar kumburi na tsarin, wanda ke nuna sakin jerin cytokines, gami da TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, da MCP-1.
Waɗannan sunadarai suna sa ƙwayoyin jikinmu su saki 'yan tsiraru masu yawa, waɗanda suke da muhimmanci wajen sa mu kamu da cutar RSA da kuma rashin ƙarfi.
Immunosuppression na da mahimmanci wajen kula da cututtukan cytokine, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu tsanani.
Ana amfani da maganin corticosteroids da tocilizumab, wani maganin rigakafin IL6 na monoclonal don magance cutar cytokine.
Sauran magungunan hana rigakafi don ruwan kwararar cytokine sun haɗa da daidaitawar amsawar rigakafi da aka yi niyya ga ƙwayoyin T; toshe IFN-y, IL-1, da TNF; hana JAKs, blinatumomab; mai hana siginar cytokine 4; da masu hana HDAC.
Ana amfani da steroids, a matsayin maganin hana rigakafi, a cikin maganin SARS don rage tsananin lalacewar kumburi.
