Bugu da ƙari ga abin rufe fuska, ya kamata ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya su saka rigunan keɓewa don rage hulɗa da cutar.
Ƙwayoyin cuta kuma suna iya shafan mutum ta idanunsa.
A ranar 22 ga Janairu, 2020, wani likita ya kamu da cutar SARS-CoV-2, duk da cewa yana sanye da abin rufe fuska na N95; cutar na iya shiga jikinsa ta hanyar idanunsa masu kumburi.
Saboda haka, ya kamata ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya su saka takunkumin fuska ko tabarau masu kariya sa'ad da suke kula da marasa lafiya.
Ga jama'a a yankunan da cutar ta shafa ko kuma za ta iya shafawa, an bada shawara sosai cewa kowa ya wanke hannuwansa da sabulu mai kashe ƙwayoyin cuta fiye da yadda ya kamata, ya yi kokarin zama a gida a keɓe, kuma ya rage hulɗa da mutanen da ke da cutar.
An ɗauki mita ɗaya a matsayin nisa da ya dace don nisanta mutum daga mai ciwo.
Waɗannan ayyuka ne masu tasiri wajen rage haɗarin kamuwa da cuta da kuma hana yaduwar cutar.
Kodayake SARS-CoV-2 ya fito ne a matsayin sabon kwayar cutar ga mutane, babban kamaninsa da SARS-CoV, kamar yadda aka ruwaito a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, ya kamata ya haifar da babban gargadi ga China bisa ga tarihinta na kwanan nan tare da annobar SARS a 2003.
A halin yanzu, har zuwa 19 ga Janairu, 2020, darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Wuhan ya kwantar da hankalin jama'a, yana cewa sabon kwayar cutar tana da ƙarancin yaduwa da iyakantaccen haifuwa tsakanin mutane, kuma ba shi da wahala a hana da kuma shawo kan cutar.
Wannan sakon ya sa mutane su huta, musamman a lokacin da kasar ke shirin bikin bazara, kuma lokacin da ake bukatar a hana cutar a Wuhan ya yi kasa.
Hukumomin kula da cututtuka a China za su iya amfani da wannan darasi mai wuya kuma su yi gagarumin ci gaba a nan gaba.
Alal misali, waɗannan hukumomi su: (1) kasance masu taka tsantsan wajen yin jawabai ga jama'a, tun da duk abin da suke faɗa yana shafan 'yan ƙasa kuma yana iya rinjayar halayensu da shawarwarinsu; (2) su kasance masu saukin kai da kuma amsawa ga bayanai masu ban mamaki daga asibitoci, maimakon jiran sanarwar hukuma daga likitoci da hukumomi; (3) su kasance masu ƙuntatawa don hana yiwuwar annobar a farkon matakin ta, maimakon ƙoƙarin ta'azantar da jama'a; da (4) fitowa da yawa kuma a kai a kai don ingantaccen siminti don ƙara wayar da kan jama'a game da cututtukan annoba da gwadawa da inganta tsarin mayar da martani na al'umma a kai a kai.
Cutar COVID-19 da sabon kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta haifar ta fara ne a ƙarshen Disamba 2019.
A cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, ya yaɗu ko'ina cikin ƙasar Sin da kusan ƙasashe 50 a duniya a lokacin da nake rubuta wannan.
Tun da yake kwayar cutar ta yi kama da SARS-CoV, kuma alamun cutar sun yi kama da na COVID-19 da SARS, annobar COVID-19 ta haifar da jin cewa SARS ta dawo.
Duk da haka, akwai bambance-bambance masu muhimmanci tsakanin COVID-19 da SARS, waɗanda suke da muhimmanci wajen shawo kan annobar da kuma kula da marasa lafiya.
COVID-19 ya fi shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa, kuma ya fi shafar maza fiye da mata, kuma tsananin cutar da yawan mutuwa sun fi girma a cikin tsofaffi fiye da matasa.
SARS na da yawan mutuwa fiye da COVID-19 (10.91% vs. 1.44%).
Marasa lafiya da COVID-19 suna yada kwayar cutar lokacin da ba su da alamun cutar, yayin da marasa lafiya da SARS sukan yada ta lokacin da suke da ciwo mai tsanani, wanda ke haifar da wahalar hana yaduwar COVID-19 fiye da SARS.
Wannan ya bayyana, a wani ɓangare, dalilin da yasa SARS-CoV-2 ke yaduwa da sauri kuma yana shafar yankuna da yawa fiye da SARS-CoV.
Gwajin RNA na yau da kullun don SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mara kyau a wasu marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19.
A wani bangare kuma, marasa lafiya da suka warke za su iya sake gwadawa da cutar.
Waɗannan sakamakon sun ƙara haɗarin yaduwar cutar sosai.
Ganin yadda bincike kan COVID-19 ke ci gaba da sauri, akwai wasu muhimman tambayoyi da har yanzu ke bukatar a warware su kamar haka:
Daga ina SARS-CoV-2 ya fito?
Ko da yake an sami kwayar halitta mai kashi 96 cikin ɗari tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da CoVs biyu na SARS-like na namomin kaza, ba za mu iya kammala cewa SARS-CoV-2 ya samo asali ne daga namomin kaza ba.
Wane dabba ne ya kawo cutar daga mahaifar da ta fara, wato, bat, zuwa ga 'yan Adam?
Idan ba mu san amsoshin tambayoyi na 1 da na 2 ba, ba za mu iya kashe watsawa yadda ya kamata ba, kuma annobar za ta iya sake faruwa a kowane lokaci.
Ko da yake ƙirar ƙwayoyin halitta da gwaje-gwajen kwayoyin sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana ɗaure da ECA2, ta yaya ainihin ƙwayar cutar take shiga cikin ƙwayoyin numfashi kuma ta haifar da canje-canje na rashin lafiya?
Shin kwayar cutar tana ɗaure da ƙwayoyin da ke nuna ECA2 a wasu gabobin?
Idan ba mu da amsoshi masu kyau ga waɗannan tambayoyin ba, ba za mu iya samun ganewar asali da kuma magani mai kyau ba.
Har yaushe za a ci gaba da annobar?
Ta yaya ne kwayar cutar take ci gaba a tsarin halittar jikinta yayin da take yaduwa tsakanin mutane?
Zai zama annoba ta duniya, zai shuɗe kamar SARS, ko kuma zai sake faruwa a yanayi kamar mura?
Yana da muhimmanci, amma zai ɗauki lokaci kafin a sami amsoshin waɗannan tambayoyin da kuma wasu da yawa.
Amma duk da haka, duk da kokarin da ake bukata, ba mu da wani zabi sai dai mu dakatar da annobar da wuri-wuri kuma mu koma rayuwarmu ta yau da kullum.
Tushen kwayar cutar korona ta mutum
Canji da daidaitawa sun haifar da coevolution na coronaviruses (CoVs) da kuma masu masaukin su, ciki har da mutane, na dubban shekaru.
Kafin 2003, an san cewa kwayar cutar korona biyu na ɗan adam (HCoVs) tana haifar da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, kamar sanyi.
Cutar cutar ta SARS da ta MERS sun canza tunanin mutane game da CoVs kuma sun nuna yadda kamuwa da HCoV zai iya zama mai hallaka da kuma hallaka.
Fashewar SARS-CoV-2 a tsakiyar China a ƙarshen 2019 ya sake sanya CoVs a kan gaba kuma ya ba kowa mamaki da yawan yaduwarsu da kuma rage cutarwa idan aka kwatanta da ɗan'uwansa SARS-CoV.
Cutar HCoV ta zoonotic ce, kuma fahimtar asalin HCoVs na zoonotic yana da matukar amfani.
Yawancin HCoVs sun samo asali ne daga batsa, wanda ba su da cutar.
An kuma san masu watsawa na matsakaici na wasu HCoVs.
Gano mai watsa labaran dabbobi yana da tasiri kai tsaye kan rigakafin cututtuka a cikin mutane.
Binciken hulɗar mai watsa shiri na CoV a cikin dabbobi na iya ba da mahimman bayanai game da kwayar cutar CoV a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun ba da cikakken bayani game da bayanan da ke akwai game da HCoVs bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su, da kuma asalin su na dabbobi da kuma watsawa tsakanin jinsuna.
Wani muhimmin bincike shi ne idan muka gwada da kuma kwatanta HCoVs daban-daban daga ra'ayi na juyin halitta na kwayar cutar da kuma sake hada kwayoyin halitta.
An tattauna game da cutar CoV 2019 (COVID-19) a wannan mahallin.
Bugu da ƙari, an kuma nuna bukatun sauyawa mai inganci tsakanin masu watsawa da kuma tasirin ci gaban kwayar cutar akan tsananin cutar.
Kwayar cuta ta coronaviruses (CoVs) na cikin dangin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na ƙwayoyin cuta masu ƙyalli, masu kyau da kuma RNA guda ɗaya.
Waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta da ke da babban kwayar halitta, tsakanin kilobases 26 zuwa 32, tsakanin ƙwayoyin cuta na RNA an kira su "CoVs" saboda tsarin jikin su na kambi lokacin da aka duba su a cikin siginar lantarki.
Game da tsari, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halittar da ba su da rarrabuwa da suke da tsari iri ɗaya.
Kimanin kashi biyu bisa uku na kwayoyin sun ƙunshi tsarin buɗe karatu guda biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b), waɗanda aka fassara su zuwa polyproteins pp1a da pp1ab.
Ana sake sarrafa polyproteins kuma suna samar da sunadarai 16 marasa tsari da ake kira nsp1 zuwa nsp16.
Sauran ɓangaren kwayoyin sun ƙunshi ORFs don sunadarai na tsari, ciki har da spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M), da nucleoprotein (N).
Wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman na ƙwayoyin cuta suna yin kwafi ta hanyoyi daban-daban na CoVs.
Dangane da bambancin jerin sunayen sunadarai, ana rarraba CoVs zuwa jinsi huɗu (alphaCoV, betaCoV, gammaCoV, da deltaCoV), daga cikinsu, betaCoV yana ɗauke da yawancin HCoVs kuma an rarraba shi zuwa jinsi huɗu (A, B, C, da D).
Bayanan ilimin halittu sun nuna cewa batsa da masu yin ɓarna suna ba da tushen kwayoyin halitta ga mafi yawan alphaCoVs da betaCoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye su ne babban wurin ajiyar gamaCoVs da deltaCoVs.
Shekaru dubbai, CoVs suna ta ƙetare iyakar jinsin, kuma wasu sun zama cututtuka masu muhimmanci ga mutane.
A yanzu haka, an san mutane bakwai da ke dauke da kwayar cutar HCoVs.
Daga cikinsu, HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 sune alphaCoVs.
Sauran betaCoVs guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, cutar coronavirus mai saurin numfashi (SARS-CoV), cutar coronavirus na numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV), da kuma SARS-CoV-2.
Kwayoyin cutar HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 galibi suna haifar da ƙananan alamomi, kamar sanyi na yau da kullun da / ko zawo.
A gefe guda, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da sabon SARS-CoV-2 masu kamuwa da cuta ne sosai kuma suna haifar da kamuwa da cuta mai tsanani a ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi a cikin marasa lafiya da yawa, tare da babban damar samun ciwon rashin jin daɗi na numfashi (ARDS) da kuma bayyanar da ke bayan huhu.
An ware kwayar cutar HCoV-229E ta farko, B814, daga jikin marasa lafiya da ke fama da mura a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin ilimi ta hanyar nazarin HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, dukansu suna haifar da alamun iyakance kansu.
A gaskiya ma, an yarda da ra'ayin cewa kamuwa da HCoVs ba shi da lahani har zuwa barkewar cutar SARS.
Annobar SARS da ta auku a shekara ta 2003 tana ɗaya daga cikin munanan annobar da aka taɓa yi, ta yi wa mutane fiye da 8,000, cutar ta kashe mutane kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 a lokacin da aka tabbatar da cutar.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, annobar cutar MERS ta Gabas ta Tsakiya ta haifar da ci gaba a yankin Larabawa, da kuma yaduwa a wasu wurare a duniya.
Sabuwar kwayar cutar HCoV ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), wanda daga baya aka sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2, shine mai haddasa annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wacce ta kashe sama da rayuka 3,120 kuma ta kamu da mutane sama da 91,000 har zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020.
An yi gargadin cewa, duniya tana bukatar ta shirya kanta domin annobar SARS-CoV-2 da ke zuwa.
Dukkanin kwayar cutar HCoVs bakwai sun samo asali ne daga batsa, mice, ko dabbobi.
Shaidu da yawa sun tabbatar da asalin juyin halitta na dukkan HCoVs daga batsa, inda ƙwayoyin cuta suka dace kuma ba su da cutar amma suna nuna bambancin kwayoyin halitta.
Cutar COVID-19 ta kawo kalubale na likita, kimiyya, zamantakewa da ɗabi'a ga Sin da sauran duniya.
Binciken asalin HCoVs na dabbobi yana ba da tsari don fahimtar tarihin halitta, ƙarfin motsawa, da abubuwan da ke hana ƙaurawar kwayar cutar zuwa wasu nau'ikan.
Wannan kuma zai iya jagorantar da sauƙaƙa bincike ta hanyar masu riƙe, matsakaici da kuma masu haɓaka SARS-CoV-2, tare da mahimman abubuwan da ke tattare da hana ƙaurawar ƙwayoyin cuta tsakanin jinsuna a nan gaba.
A cikin wannan labarin, mun ba da cikakken bayani game da asalin dabbobi, watsawa tsakanin jinsuna, da kuma cutar HCoVs.
Musamman, mun nuna kuma mun tattauna batun gama gari cewa ƙwayoyin cuta na HCoVs ba su da cutar a cikin mahaifansu na halitta amma sun zama masu cutar bayan watsawa tsakanin jinsuna zuwa sabon mai masauki.
Mun kuma duba yanayin juyin HCoV, wanda yawanci yawan yaduwar cutar yana tare da raguwar cutar.
Ana kuma tattauna sakamakon annobar SARS-CoV-2 na yanzu a wannan mahallin.
An san CoVs na dabbobi tun daga ƙarshen shekarun 1930.
Kafin farkon ware kwayar cutar B814 na HCoV-229E daga kwayar cutar daga marasa lafiya da suka kamu da mura, an gano CoVs daban-daban a cikin dabbobi da dama da suka kamu da cutar, ciki har da turkey, mice, shanu, alade, kuli, da kare.
A cikin shekarun baya bayan nan, an gano kwayar cutar HCoVs bakwai.
Takaitaccen tarihin gano HCoV cikin tsari na lokaci (Table 1) zai kasance mai bayani da kuma koyarwa.
An fara ware kwayar HCoV-229E daga cikin numfashi na marasa lafiya da ke da kamuwa da cutar numfashi a shekarar 1966, kuma daga baya aka daidaita ta don girma a cikin ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin WI-38 na huhu.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da HCoV-229E sun nuna alamun sanyi na yau da kullun, gami da ciwon kai, tari, rashin jin daɗi da ciwon makogwaro, tare da zazzabi da tari a cikin kashi 10% zuwa 20% na lokuta.
Daga baya, a 1967, an ware HCoV-OC43 daga al'adun gabobin jiki da kuma jerin abubuwan da suka biyo baya a cikin kwakwalwar linzamin kwamfuta.
Halin asibiti na kamuwa da HCoV-OC43 ya yi kama da wanda HCoV-229E ke haifarwa, wanda ba shi da bambanci daga kamuwa da wasu cututtukan cututtukan numfashi, kamar su ƙwayoyin cuta na mura A da rhinoviruses.
HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 suna da rarraba a duniya, kuma suna yaduwa a lokacin hunturu a yanayin zafi.
A gaba ɗaya, lokacin ɓoyewar waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta guda biyu bai kai mako ɗaya ba, tare da ciwon da ke tare da cutar na kusan makonni 2.
Dangane da binciken da aka yi kan masu sa kai na mutane, mutane masu lafiya da ke kamuwa da HCoV-229E sun sami sanyi mai sauƙi.
Wasu marasa lafiya ne kawai da ke da rashin lafiyar jiki suka kamu da cutar numfashi mai tsanani.
SARS, wanda aka fi sani da "atypical pneumonia", shi ne annoba ta farko da aka rubuta cewa HCoV ne ya haifar da shi a tarihin ɗan adam, kuma kwayar cutar SARS-CoV ce, HCoV na uku da aka gano.
An samu farkon cutar SARS a shekara ta 2002 a lardin Guangdong na kasar Sin.
Annobar SARS ta haifar da karuwar mutane 8,096 da suka kamu da cutar tare da mutuwar mutane 774, ta bazu a kasashe da nahiyoyi da dama.
Sai dai ga "super-spreaders", an kiyasta cewa kowane mutum mai kamuwa da cutar zai iya kamuwa da wasu mutane biyu, tare da tsawon kwana 4 zuwa 7, kuma tare da bayyanar ƙaruwar ƙwayar cutar a rana ta goma na cutar.
Marasa lafiya da ke dauke da SARS-CoV suna fara nuna ciwon zuciya, ciwon kai, zazzabi, rashin jin daɗi da kuma jin zafin jiki, sannan kuma suna nuna alamun rashin nutsuwa, tari da rashin jin daɗin numfashi.
Lymphopenia, rashin aikin hanta da kuma yawan creatine kinase su ne cututtukan SARS da aka saba samu a gwajin gwaji.
An kuma lura da lalacewar alveolar da ke yaduwa, yaduwar ƙwayoyin epithelial da kuma ƙaruwar macrophage a cikin marasa lafiya da SARS.
Kusan kashi 20 zuwa 30 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya suna bukatar kulawa mai tsanani da kuma na'ura mai aiki da iska a wani lokaci.
Baya ga ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi, wasu gabobin ciki har da gastrointestinal tract, hanta da koda, suma za a iya shafar su a cikin waɗannan mawuyacin yanayi, yawanci ta hanyar fitowar cytokine, wanda zai iya zama mai kisa, musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu rauni.
An fara gano kwayar cutar ne a jikin wani dan uwan marasa lafiya Zero da ke tafiya daga Guangzhou zuwa Hong Kong.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an yi ƙoƙari sosai wajen bincike kan HCoV.
An ware HCoV-NL63 daga jariri mai wata 7 a Netherlands a ƙarshen 2004.
An fara gano cewa cutar ta fi yawa a cikin yara ƙanana, tsofaffi, da marasa lafiya masu rashin garkuwar jiki da ke fama da cututtukan numfashi.
Alamun rashin lafiya na cutar HCoV-NL63 sun hada da rashin lafiyar zuciya, cutar haɗiye, zazzabi da kuma ciwon huhu.
Wani bincike na 'yanci ya bayyana ware irin wannan kwayar cutar daga kwayar hanci na jariri mai wata takwas da ke fama da ciwon huhu a Netherlands.
Ko da yake an gano shi a ƙasar Holland, amma ya yaɗu a dukan duniya.
An kiyasta cewa HCoV-NL63 ya yi daidai da kusan kashi 4.7% na cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun, kuma yawan su yana ƙaruwa a lokacin hunturu, bazara da farkon bazara.
HCoV-NL63 yana da alaƙa da cutar larynxitis, wanda kuma ake kira croup.
A wannan shekarar, an ware HCoV-HKU1 daga wani mutum mai shekaru 71 da aka kwantar da shi da ciwon huhu da kuma ciwon huhu a Hong Kong.
Baya ga ciwon huhu da kuma ciwon daji na gari, an ba da rahoton cewa HCoV-HKU1 yana da alaƙa da ƙaruwar cutar asma.
Kamar yadda HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 suka kasance, an sami HCoV-HKU1 a duk duniya, yana haifar da cututtukan numfashi masu saurin kamuwa da cuta.
Dukkanin wadannan kwayar cutar HCoVs guda hudu da aka samu a cikin al'umma sun daidaita da kyau ga mutane kuma suna da karancin damar canzawa da haifar da cututtuka masu saurin kamuwa da cuta, kodayake haɗari sun faru saboda dalilai da ba a sani ba a cikin wani ɗan ƙaramin nau'in nau'in HCoV-NL63 wanda aka ba da rahoton kwanan nan a matsayin mai haifar da mummunar kamuwa da ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi a China.
Gabaɗaya, lokacin da waɗannan HCoVs suka sami damar watsawa cikin inganci kuma suna ci gaba da kasancewa cikin mutane, suma suna zama masu ƙarancin ƙwayoyin cuta da ƙarancin ƙwayoyin cuta.
An fara ware MERS-CoV a shekarar 2012 daga huhu na wani mai shekaru 60 da haihuwa wanda ya kamu da ciwon huhu mai tsanani da kuma rashin aikin koda a Saudi Arabia.
Yayin da yawancin magungunan da aka tabbatar da su daga Gabas ta Tsakiya ne, an samu rahoton shigo da magungunan da ke da saurin yaduwa ta hanyar kusanci a ƙasashen Turai da Tunisia.
Wani annoba na biyu ya faru a Koriya ta Kudu a 2015 tare da tabbatar da mutane 186.
Bayyanar asibiti na MERS suna kama da na SARS, wanda ke nuna ci gaba da ciwon huhu mai tsanani.
Ba kamar SARS ba, marasa lafiya da yawa da ke da cutar MERS suna samun rashin aikin koda, wanda hakan ya sa MERS ta zama ta musamman a cikin cututtukan da HCoVs ke haifarwa.
Fiye da kashi 30 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya suna da alamun ciwon ciki, kamar su zawo da kuma zubar da ciki.
Har zuwa 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, sama da lambobi 2,500 da aka tabbatar da su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje an bayar da rahoton su tare da yawan mutuwar da ke da nasaba da wadanda aka tabbatar da su, na kashi 34.4%, wanda ya sanya MERS-CoV daya daga cikin cututtukan da suka fi muni da aka sani ga dan Adam.
Daga tsakiyar zuwa ƙarshen Disamba 2019, an gano rukunin marasa lafiya da ke da ciwon huhu, wanda aka san cewa yana da alaƙa da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana annobar cutar na ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi da SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa a matsayin gaggawa ta lafiyar jama'a mai muhimmanci a duniya, kuma ta sanya sunan cutar COVID-19.
Har zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020, an tabbatar da mutane 90,053 a duniya, tare da yawan mutuwar da ke da alaƙa da waɗanda aka tabbatar da kashi 3.4%.
An lura cewa mutuwar da ke tattare da waɗanda aka tabbatar da su a Hubei, China, ya kai kashi 4.2 cikin ɗari, yayin da mutuwar da ke wajen wannan birni ta kai kashi 1.2 cikin ɗari.
SARS-CoV-2 na haifar da mummunar kamuwa da cuta ta numfashi, kamar yadda SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV suke, tare da zazzabi, tari da kuma dyspnea.
Wasu marasa lafiya ma suna da zawo.
Ciwon huhu yana cikin munanan alamu kuma yana iya saurin zama ciwo mai tsanani na numfashi.
Kodayake SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da kamanceceniya sosai saboda babban daidaito na 82% a cikin jerin nucleotides, sun haɗu a cikin rassa daban-daban a cikin bishiyar phylogenetic.
SARS-CoV-2 a bayyane yake ba shi da cutar amma yana da yaduwa idan aka kwatanta da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
An samu rahotanni na mutane marasa alamun cutar SARS-CoV-2, kuma suna iya taimakawa wajen saurin yaduwar cutar a duniya.
Kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da sauran HCoVs shida sun nuna kamance da bambance-bambance masu mahimmanci.
Na farko, lokacin da cutar HCoV take kwance da kuma tsawon lokacin da take gudana suna da kama sosai.
A wannan ma'anar, SARS-CoV-2 yana bin babban yanayin sauran HCoVs shida.
