Kamfanin da ke yin takardar wanka mai sake amfani da ita mai suna Who Gives a Crap ya ce a ranar Laraba da ta gabata cewa ba su da isassun kayayyaki.
Kamfanin Kimberly-Clark, wanda ke samar da takardar wanka ta Kleenex, da Solaris Paper, wanda ke samar da Sorbent, sun jaddada cewa suna aiki 24 a rana, 7 a mako don ci gaba da samar da kayayyaki, kamar yadda News.com.au ta ruwaito.
Shafin yanar gizo na dukiya domain.com ya ruwaito cewa wasu masu sayar da gidaje suna ba da takardar bayan gida kyauta ga masu fara siyar da kaya a Melbourne, lokacin da aka fara yin siyarwa kaɗan tare da masu siye da suka shiga hutu a ƙarshen ranar Labor Day.
Mujallar NT News ta ranar Alhamis, jaridar Darwin ta yau da kullum, ta haɗa da wani shafi mai shafuffuka takwas da aka shirya a yanka shi kuma a yi amfani da shi a matsayin takardar wanka.
