Amfani da kalmar "rabuwa da jama'a" ya haifar da ma'anar cewa ana buƙatar keɓewar jama'a gaba ɗaya maimakon ƙarfafa tuntuɓar ta wasu hanyoyin. Wasu jami'ai sun buga jagororin kiwon lafiya na jima'i yayin annobar.
Waɗannan shawarwarin sun haɗa da yin jima'i da wanda kuke zama da shi kawai, wanda ba shi da cutar ko kuma alamun cutar.
An ba da shawarar ware kai a gida ga waɗanda aka gano suna da COVID-19 da waɗanda suke zargin cewa suna da cutar.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya sun ba da cikakkun bayanai game da keɓe kai yadda ya kamata. Gwamnatoci da yawa sun bukaci ko sun ba da shawarar keɓe kai ga dukan mutanen da ke zaune a yankunan da cutar ta shafa.
