Ana zargin cewa masu bautar Shincheonji da suka ziyarci Daegu daga Wuhan ne suka fara barkewar cutar.
A ranar 22 ga Fabrairu, daga cikin masu bin cocin 9,336, 1,261, ko kuma kusan kashi 13 cikin ɗari na su, sun ba da rahoton cewa suna da alamun cutar.
