Iran ta tabbatar da farkon kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 19 ga Fabrairu a Qom, inda a cewar Ma'aikatar Lafiya da Ilimin Likita, mutane biyu suka mutu a wannan rana.
Matakan farko da gwamnati ta sanar sun hada da soke kide kide da wake-wake da sauran al'amuran al'adu, wasanni, da kuma bukukuwan addini a ranakun Juma'a, rufe jami'o'i, cibiyoyin ilimi, da makarantu.
Iran ta ba da tiriliyan biyar na Riyal don yaki da cutar.
Shugaba Hassan Rouhani ya ce a ranar 26 ga Fabrairu, 2020 cewa ba shi da wani shiri game da yankunan da cutar ta shafa, kuma za a sanya mutane ne kawai a cikin keɓewa.
An sanar da tsare-tsaren rage tafiye-tafiye tsakanin biranen a watan Maris, duk da cewa ana ci gaba da samun cunkoso a tsakanin biranen kafin Sabuwar Shekarar Farisa Nowruz.
Wuraren ibada na Shi'a a Qom sun kasance a bude ga mahajjata har zuwa 16 ga Maris, 2020. Iran ta zama cibiyar yaduwar cutar bayan China a watan Fabrairu.
A cikin zargin rufewa game da yaduwar cutar a Iran, sama da kasashe goma sun bi diddigin wadanda suka shafi Iran a ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu inda suka nuna cewa yaduwar cutar na iya zama mafi muni fiye da 388 da gwamnatin Iran ta ruwaito zuwa wannan ranar.
An rufe majalisar dokokin Iran, tare da 23 daga cikin mambobinta 290 da suka gwada tabbatacce ga kwayar cutar a ranar 3 ga Maris.
A ranar 12 ga watan Maris, Human Rights Watch ta yi kira ga hukumomin gidan yari na Iran da su saki masu kare hakkin bil'adama da aka tsare saboda rashin amincewa da zaman lafiya, da kuma sake duk fursunonin da suka cancanci hakan.
Hukumar ta ce akwai babbar barazanar yaduwar cutar a cibiyoyin da aka rufe kamar cibiyoyin tsare mutane, wadanda kuma ke fama da rashin kulawar likita.
A ranar 15 ga watan Maris, gwamnatin Iran ta bayar da rahoton mutuwar mutane 100 a rana guda, wanda shi ne mafi girma tun lokacin da annobar ta barke a kasar.
Akalla 'yan siyasa 12 da suka yi ritaya da jami'an gwamnati sun mutu sakamakon cutar har zuwa ranar 17 ga watan Maris.
Har zuwa 23 ga Maris, Iran tana da sabbin mutane 50 a kowace awa kuma tana da sabon mutum daya da ke mutuwa a kowane minti goma saboda cutar coronavirus.
A cewar wani wakilin WHO, akwai yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar sau biyar a Iran fiye da yadda ake ruwaitowa.
An nuna cewa takunkumin Amurka kan Iran na iya shafar ikon kasar wajen magance annobar cutar.
Babban Kwamishinan 'Yancin Dan Adam ya bukaci a sassauta takunkumin tattalin arziki ga kasashen da cutar ta fi shafa, ciki har da Iran.
An tabbatar da barkewar cutar a Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu, lokacin da wasu 'yan yawon bude ido biyu na kasar Sin suka gwada tabbatacciyar cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Rome.
Cutar ta fara ƙaruwa sosai, wanda ya sa gwamnatin Italiya ta dakatar da duk jiragen da ke zuwa da kuma daga China kuma ta ayyana dokar ta baci.
An gano wani rukunin da ba shi da alaƙa da shari'o'in COVID-19 daga baya, farawa da 16 da aka tabbatar a Lombardy a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu. A ranar 22 ga Fabrairu, Majalisar Ministoci ta sanar da dokar da za ta hana barkewar cutar, gami da keɓe mutane sama da 50,000 daga gundumomi 11 daban-daban a arewacin Italiya.
Firayim Minista Giuseppe Conte ya ce, "A yankunan da cutar ta bulla, an hana mutane shiga da fita.
An riga an yanke shawarar dakatar da ayyukan aiki da wasannin motsa jiki a waɗannan yankuna. "A ranar 4 ga Maris, gwamnatin Italiya ta nemi a rufe dukkan makarantu da jami'o'i a duk faɗin ƙasar lokacin da Italiya ta kai mutuwar 100.
Duk manyan wasannin wasanni, ciki har da wasannin kwallon kafa na Serie A, dole ne a gudanar da su a rufe har zuwa watan Afrilu, amma a ranar 9 ga Maris, an dakatar da duk wasannin wasanni gaba daya na akalla wata daya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Conte ya nemi a rufe kusan dukkan ayyukan kasuwanci, sai dai manyan kantuna da kantunan magani. A ranar 6 ga Maris, Kwalejin Kula da Magunguna, Analgesia, Resuscitation da Intensive Care (SIAARTI) ta buga shawarwarin ɗabi'a game da hanyoyin da za a iya amfani da su.
A ranar 19 ga Maris, Italiya ta zarce China a matsayin kasa da ke da yawan mutuwar Coronavirus a duniya bayan ta bayar da rahoton mutuwar 3,405 da ke da nasaba da annobar.
A ranar 22 ga watan Maris, an sanar da cewa Rasha ta aika da jiragen sama na soja tara dauke da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya zuwa Italiya.
Ya zuwa ranar 5 ga Afrilu, akwai mutane 128,948 da aka tabbatar da su, 15,887 sun mutu, 21,815 kuma sun warke a Italiya, tare da mafi yawan waɗannan masu cutar a yankin Lombardy.
Wani rahoto na CNN ya nuna cewa haɗuwa da tsofaffi a Italiya da kuma rashin iya gwada duk wanda ya kamu da cutar a lokacin na iya taimakawa wajen yawan mutuwar.
Amsar Burtaniya ga cutar ta fito ne da farko a matsayin daya daga cikin mafi sauki a cikin kasashen da cutar ta shafa, kuma har zuwa ranar 18 ga Maris, 2020, gwamnatin Burtaniya ba ta sanya kowane irin nau'in nisantar zamantakewa ko matakan keɓewa ga jama'arta ba.
A sakamakon haka, gwamnati ta fuskanci suka saboda rashin kulawa da kuma karfin martani ga matsalolin da jama'a ke fuskanta. A ranar 16 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Boris Johnson ya yi jawabi inda ya ba da shawarar dakatar da duk tafiye-tafiye marasa mahimmanci da hulɗa da jama'a, yana ba da shawarar mutane suyi aiki a gida kamar yadda zai yiwu kuma su guji wurare kamar mashaya, gidajen cin abinci da gidajen wasan kwaikwayo.
A ranar 20 ga Maris, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa duk wuraren shakatawa kamar mashaya da dakunan motsa jiki dole ne a rufe su da wuri-wuri, kuma sun yi alƙawarin biyan kashi 80% na albashin ma'aikata har zuwa iyakar £ 2,500 a wata don kauce wa rashin aikin yi a lokacin rikicin. A ranar 23 ga Maris, Firayim Minista ya sanar da matakan nisantar zamantakewar jama'a, hana tarurruka da mutane sama da biyu da kuma takaita tafiye-tafiye da ayyukan waje zuwa mafi ƙarancin abin da ake buƙata.
Ba kamar matakan da suka gabata ba, 'yan sanda sun ƙara tsaurara waɗannan ƙuntatawa ta hanyar yin tara da kuma tarwatsa ƙauyuka.
An umarci yawancin kasuwancin da za su rufe, sai dai ga waɗanda aka ce "masu muhimmanci", kamar su kantunan sayar da kayayyaki, kantin magani, bankuna, kantunan kayan aiki, kantunan mai da motoci da kuma wuraren gyaran motoci.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an tabbatar da mutum na farko da aka sani da cutar COVID-19 a jihar Washington ta Arewa maso Yammacin Pacific a cikin wani mutum da ya dawo daga Wuhan a ranar 15 ga Janairu.
An kafa rundunar White House don yaki da cutar korona a ranar 29 ga watan Janairu.
A ranar 31 ga watan Janairu, gwamnatin Trump ta ayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya, kuma ta sanya takunkumin shiga matafiya daga China.
A ranar 28 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka  babbar cibiyar kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta gwamnatin Amurka  ta sanar da cewa sun kirkiro kayan gwajin nasu.
Duk da cewa sun yi hakan, Amurka ta fara gwajin ne a hankali, wanda hakan ya ɓoye ainihin yaduwar cutar a lokacin.
Gwajin ya kasance da alamun rashin ingantattun kayan gwajin da gwamnatin tarayya ta samar a watan Fabrairu, rashin amincewar gwamnatin tarayya ga kayan gwajin da ba na gwamnati ba (daga dakunan motsa jiki, kamfanoni da asibitoci) har zuwa karshen watan Fabrairu, da kuma takunkumin takunkumi ga mutanen da za a gwada su har zuwa farkon watan Maris (ana buƙatar umarnin likita daga baya).
Har zuwa ranar 27 ga Fabrairu, jaridar Washington Post ta ba da rahoton cewa an yi gwaje-gwaje kasa da 4,000 a Amirka.
Har zuwa 13 ga Maris, jaridar The Atlantic ta ba da rahoton cewa an yi gwaji kasa da 14,000.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, Associated Press ta ba da rahoto: "Mutane da yawa da suke da alamun cutar kuma suna da bukatar likita sun jira sa'o'i ko kwanaki kafin a gwada su". Bayan an ba da rahoton mutuwar farko a Amurka a jihar Washington a ranar 29 ga Fabrairu, Gwamna Jay Inslee ya ayyana dokar ta baci, kuma wasu jihohi sun bi wannan matakin.
Makarantu a yankin Seattle sun soke karatu a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma a karo na biyu na Maris, makarantu a duk faɗin ƙasar suna rufewa. A ranar 6 ga Maris, 2020, an gargadi Amurka game da hasashen tasirin sabon coronavirus a cikin ƙasar ta hanyar ƙungiyar masana cututtuka daga Kwalejin Imperial ta London.
A wannan rana, Shugaba Trump ya sanya hannu kan Dokar Karin Tallafi na Shirye-shiryen da Amsa da Cutar Korona, wanda ya ba da dala biliyan 8.3 a matsayin asusun gaggawa ga hukumomin tarayya a matsayin martani ga annobar.
Kamfanoni sun kafa takunkumin hana ma'aikata tafiya, sun soke taro, kuma sun ƙarfafa ma'aikata su yi aiki daga gida.
An soke abubuwan wasanni da lokutan wasanni. A ranar 11 ga Maris, Trump ya sanar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye zuwa mafi yawan Turai, tare da cire Burtaniya, na tsawon kwanaki 30, daga ranar 13 ga Maris.
Washegari, ya faɗaɗa takunkumin zuwa ƙasar Ingila da kuma Ireland.
A ranar 13 ga watan Maris, ya ayyana dokar ta-baci, wanda hakan ya sa aka samu kudaden tarayya don magance matsalar.
Farawa daga ranar 15 ga watan Maris, kamfanoni da dama sun rufe ko rage ayyukansu a duk fadin Amurka domin kokarin rage yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga Maris, an tabbatar da annobar a jihohi 50 da Gundumar Columbia. A ranar 23 ga Maris, an bayar da rahoton cewa birnin New York yana da mutane 10,700 da suka kamu da cutar, fiye da adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar a Koriya ta Kudu.
A ranar 25 ga Maris, gwamnan ya ce ya yi kamar nisantar mutane yana aiki, yayin da kimar ninka yawan masu kamuwa da cutar ya ragu daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa kwanaki 4.7.
A ranar 28 ga watan Maris, an tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar a birnin New York, inda mutane 32,308 suka kamu, kuma mutane 672 suka mutu sakamakon cutar. A ranar 26 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta bayar da rahoton kamuwa da cutar fiye da kowace kasa a duniya, ciki har da China da Italiya. A ranar 8 ga watan Afrilu, an tabbatar da kamuwa da cutar a Amurka, kuma mutane 12,841 sun mutu.
Rahotanni na kafofin watsa labarai sun ce a ranar 30 ga watan Maris, Shugaba Trump na Amurka ya yanke shawarar tsawaita dokokin nisantar juna har zuwa ranar 30 ga watan Afrilu.
A wannan rana, jirgin asibiti mai suna USNS Comfort, mai gado 1,000, ya sauka a New York.
A ranar 3 ga Afrilu, Amurka ta samu adadin mutuwar mutane 884 da cutar coronavirus ta yi a cikin sa'o'i 24.
A jihar New York, mutane sun zarce 100,000 a ranar 3 ga Afrilu. An soki fadar White House da ta raina barazanar da kuma sarrafa aika sakonni ta hanyar umarci jami'an kiwon lafiya da masana kimiyya da su daidaita wallafe-wallafen jama'a da maganganun da suka shafi kwayar cutar zuwa ofishin Mataimakin Shugaban Kasa Mike Pence.
An samu amincewa da yadda Trump ya gudanar da rikicin a bangarori daban-daban.
Wasu jami'an Amurka da masu sharhi sun soki amincewar Amurka kan shigo da kayan masarufi, ciki har da kayan kiwon lafiya, daga China.
An yi amfani da nazarin halayen tafiye-tafiye na iska don yin taswira da hasashen yanayin yaduwa kuma an buga shi a cikin The Journal of Travel Medicine a tsakiyar Janairu 2020.
Dangane da bayanan 2018 na Kungiyar Sufurin Jiragen Sama ta Duniya, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo da Taipei sun sami mafi yawan matafiya daga Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney da Melbourne kuma an bayar da rahoton cewa sune wuraren da mutane ke zuwa da suka tashi daga Wuhan.
An bayar da rahoton Bali a matsayin mafi ƙarancin iyawa a cikin shahararrun wurare 20 dangane da shiri, yayin da birane a Ostiraliya aka yi la'akari da mafi iyawa. Ostiraliya ta ba da izinin Tsarin Amsa na Gaggawa don Sabon Coronavirus (COVID-19) a ranar 7 ga Fabrairu.
Ta bayyana cewa har yanzu akwai abubuwa da yawa da za a gano game da COVID-19, kuma cewa Ostiraliya za ta jaddada kula da kan iyakoki da sadarwa a cikin amsar cutar.
A ranar 21 ga watan Maris, an ayyana gaggawa ta lafiyar ɗan adam a Ostiraliya.
Saboda ingantacciyar keɓewar sufuri na jama'a a Wuhan da Hubei, ƙasashe da dama sun shirya cire 'yan ƙasa da ma'aikatan diflomasiyya daga yankin, da farko ta hanyar jiragen haya daga ƙasar da suka fito, tare da sakin hukumomin China.
Kanada, Amurka, Japan, Indiya, Sri Lanka, Australia, Faransa, Argentina, Jamus da Thailand suna cikin na farko da suka fara shirin janye 'yan kasarsu.
Pakistan ta ce ba za ta mayar da duk wani dan kasar Sin ba.
A ranar 7 ga watan Fabrairu, Brazil ta kwashe 'yan Brazil 34 ko danginsu ban da 'yan Poland hudu, da wani dan China da kuma wani dan Indiya.
'Yan kasar Poland, China da Indiya sun sauka a Poland, inda jirgin na Brazil ya tsaya kafin ya ci gaba da tafiya zuwa Brazil.
An killace 'yan Brazil da suka tafi Wuhan a wani sansanin soji kusa da Brasília.
A wannan rana, an kwashe 'yan Kanada 215 (mai jirgin sama na farko 176, da kuma 39 na jirgin sama na biyu da gwamnatin Amurka ta yi haya) daga Wuhan kuma an tura su sansanin sojin sama na Trenton don su kasance a cikin keɓewa na makonni biyu.
A ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama mai dauke da 'yan Kanada 185 daga Wuhan ya sauka a sansanin sojin Kanada na Trenton.
Hukumomin Australiya sun kai mutane 277 a ranar 3 da 4 ga watan Fabrairu zuwa Cibiyar Tsare-tsare ta Tsibirin Kirsimeti, wanda daga baya aka sake amfani da shi a matsayin wurin keɓewa, inda suka zauna na kwanaki 14.
Jirgin saukar jiragen sama na 'yan kasar New Zealand ya sauka a Auckland a ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu; fasinjojinsa (ciki har da wasu daga Australia da Pacific) an killace su a wani sansanin sojan ruwa a Whangaparoa, arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga watan Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar da cewa za ta janye Amurkawa daga jirgin ruwan Diamond Princess.
A ranar 21 ga watan Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama dauke da fasinjoji 129 na Kanada da aka kwashe daga Diamond Princess, ya sauka a Trenton, Ontario.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Indiya ta fara kwashe 'yan kasarta daga Iran. A ranar 14 ga watan Maris, wani jirgin saman kamfanin South African Airways da gwamnatin Afirka ta Kudu ta yi haya ya dawo da 'yan kasar Afrika ta Kudu 112.
An yi gwajin lafiya kafin a shigo da jirgin, kuma an bar wasu 'yan Afirka ta Kudu huɗu da suka nuna alamun kamuwa da cutar korona a baya don rage hadarin.
Sai dai 'yan Afirka ta Kudu da suka nuna cewa ba su da cutar ne kawai aka mayar da su gida.
Sakamakon gwajin ya saki dukkan 'yan Afirka ta Kudu, ciki har da ma'aikatan jirgin, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal, 'yan sanda da sojoji da ke cikin aikin agaji wanda, a matsayin kariya, sun kasance a karkashin lura da keɓewa na tsawon kwanaki 14 a wurin shakatawa na The Ranch.
A ranar 20 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta fara janye dakarunta daga Iraki saboda annobar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar da Iran) sun aika da taimako ga kasar Sin.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin a jami'o'in Amurka sun hada kai don taimakawa wajen tura kayan agaji ga wadanda cutar ta shafa a kasar Sin, tare da wani rukuni na hadin gwiwa a yankin Greater Chicago wanda ya samu nasarar aika da takunkumin N95 dubu 50 zuwa asibitocin lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga watan Janairu. Kungiyar agaji ta Direct Relief, tare da hadin gwiwa da FedEx, ta aika da takunkumin fuska dubu 200 tare da sauran kayan kariya na mutum, ciki har da safofin hannu da sutura, ta hanyar jigilar jiragen sama na gaggawa zuwa asibitin Wuhan Union a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don tallafawa binciken allurar rigakafi da ƙoƙarin magani tare da kare "mutanen da ke cikin haɗari a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya".
Interaksyon ta ruwaito cewa gwamnatin China ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga watan Fabrairu, bayan Sanata Richard Gordon ya aika da abin rufe fuska miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta tura dala miliyan 2.26 a matsayin tallafi ga kasar Sin.
Japan ta ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska miliyan daya zuwa Wuhan, Turkiyya ta aika da kayan aikin likita, Rasha ta aika da kayan aikin kiwon lafiya sama da tan 13 zuwa Wuhan, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da gudummawar safar hannu na kiwon lafiya miliyan 18 zuwa China, Jamus ta ba da kayan aikin kiwon lafiya da dama, gami da rigunan kariya dubu 10, kuma Amurka ta ba da gudummawar tan 17.8 na kayan aikin kiwon lafiya ga China kuma ta yi alkawarin ƙarin dala miliyan 100 a matsayin tallafin kuɗi ga ƙasashen da abin ya shafa. Bayan da shari'o'in da ke China suka daidaita, kasar ta ci gaba da aika da taimako ga ƙasashe da yawa da cutar ta shafa.
A watan Maris, Sin, Cuba da Rasha sun aika da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya da kwararru don taimakawa Italiya wajen magance annobar coronavirus.
Dan kasuwa Jack Ma ya aika da kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1, da abin rufe fuska miliyan 6 da kuma tufafi masu kariya dubu 60 zuwa Addis Ababa a Habasha domin rarraba su ta hanyar kungiyar tarayyar Afirka.
Bayan haka, ya aika da kayan gwaji 5,000, da abin rufe fuska 100,000, da kuma na'urorin numfashi biyar zuwa Panama.
Ma ya kuma ba da gudummawar kayayyakin kiwon lafiya ga Kanada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia da Czech Republic sun nuna damuwa game da abin rufe fuska da kayan gwajin da aka yi a China.
Alal misali, Spain ta karɓi kayan gwajin cutar korona dubu 58 da aka yi daga China da kashi 30 cikin 100 na daidaito, yayin da Netherlands ta mayar da abin rufe fuska 600,000 da suka lalace.
Belgium ta tattara abin rufe fuska 100,000 da ba za a iya amfani da su ba, da ake zaton daga China ne, amma a zahiri daga Colombia ne.
A wani bangare kuma, an yi maraba da taimakon da kasar Sin ta bayar a sassan Latin Amurka da Afirka.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta yaba wa kokarin da hukumomin kasar Sin ke yi wajen sarrafa da kuma shawo kan annobar.
WHO ta lura da bambanci tsakanin barkewar cutar SARS ta 2002-2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin kasar Sin da watsi da bayanai da suka sa rigakafin da kokarin hana cutar ya yi wuya, da kuma rikicin na yanzu, inda gwamnatin tsakiya "ta samar da sabuntawa akai-akai don kaucewa fargaba a lokacin bukukuwan sabuwar shekara ta Lunar".
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, a mayar da martani ga shawarar manyan hukumomi na aiwatar da haramcin sufuri a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya lura cewa "wannan ba shawarar WHO ba ce" kuma "wani muhimmin nuni ne na jajircewa wajen shawo kan annobar a yankin da ta fi yawa". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan tabbatar da yaduwar tsakanin mutane a wajen China da karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a wasu kasashe, WHO ta ayyana annobar a matsayin gaggawa ta kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta duniya (PHEIC), PHEIC ta shida tun lokacin da aka fara kira da matakin a lokacin annobar cutar sankarar alade ta 2009.
Darakta Janar na WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce an kira PHEIC ne saboda "hadarin yaduwar duniya, musamman a ƙasashe masu ƙarancin kuɗi da matsakaitan kuɗi ba tare da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya ba.
A martanin da ya mayar game da aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya bayyana cewa "babu wani dalili na matakan da ke tsoma baki ba dole ba a tafiye-tafiye na kasa da kasa da kuma kasuwanci" kuma "WHO ba ta ba da shawarar a takaita kasuwanci da tafiye-tafiye ba".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya da su ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 domin tallafawa shirye-shiryen da aka tsara a ƙasashe masu karancin kuɗi da matsakaitan kuɗi, tana mai ambaton gaggawa a taimaka wa ƙasashen da "ba su da tsarin da za su iya gano mutanen da suka kamu da cutar, ko da ta taso".
Tedros ya yi maganganu na gaba yana mai cewa "mu masu ƙarfi ne kamar yadda mahaɗanmu suka raunana" kuma ya nemi al'ummar duniya "su saka hannun jari yanzu ko kuma za su biya daga baya". A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO a taron manema labarai ta kafa COVID-19 a matsayin sunan cutar.
A wannan ranar, Tedros ya bayyana cewa Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya António Guterres ya amince ya samar da "ikon dukkan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a matsayin martani".
An kunna Kungiyar Gudanar da Rikicin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a sakamakon hakan, wanda ya ba da damar daidaita duk wani martani na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda WHO ta ce zai ba su damar "mai da hankali kan mayar da hankali kan maganin kiwon lafiya yayin da sauran hukumomi za su iya shigowa da kwarewarsu kan zamantakewar al'umma, tattalin arziki da kuma ci gaban da cutar ke haifarwa".
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairu, an ba da damar ƙungiyar haɗin gwiwar WHO tare da China don samar da ƙwararrun ƙasashen duniya da na WHO a ƙasar China tare da taimakon gudanarwa na gida da kimantawa "matsanancin cutar da yaduwar cutar" ta hanyar bita da tarurruka tare da manyan cibiyoyin matakin ƙasa da kuma gudanar da ziyarar filin don kimantawa "tasirin ayyukan amsawa a matakan lardi da na gari, gami da birane da na karkara". A ranar 25 ga Fabrairu, WHO ta bayyana cewa "ya kamata duniya ta yi ƙarin shiri don yiwuwar cutar ta Coronavirus", ta bayyana cewa, kodayake da wuri don ayyana cutar, duk da haka, ƙasashe ya kamata su kafa "matakin shiri".
A cikin martani ga barkewar cutar a Iran, WHO ta aika da tawagar hadin gwiwa don tantance halin da ake ciki. A ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, jami'an WHO sun ce za a kara darajar barazanar Coronavirus a duniya daga "babba" zuwa "mai matukar girma", matakin mafi girma na faɗakarwa da kimanta hadari.
Mike Ryan, darektan shirin gaggawa na kiwon lafiya, ya yi gargadi a cikin wata sanarwa cewa "Wannan sanarwa ce ta gaskiya ga kowace gwamnati a duniya: Ku farka.
Wannan cuta na iya zuwa, kuma kuna bukatar ku kasance a shirye", yana mai cewa matakan da suka dace na amsawa zai iya taimakawa duniya ta guji "mafi munin".
Ryan ya kuma ce bayanan na yanzu ba su ba jami'an kiwon lafiyar jama'a damar bayyana annobar duniya ba, yana mai cewa irin wannan sanarwar na nufin cewa "ainihin mun yarda cewa kowane ɗan adam a duniya zai sami wannan cutar".
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, WHO ta ayyana annobar coronavirus a matsayin annoba.
