Gwajin gwaje-gwaje na cutar coronavirus na numfashi na 2019 (COVID-19) da kuma cutar SARS-CoV-2 da ke hade da shi sun hada da hanyoyin da ke gano kasancewar kwayar cutar da kuma wadanda ke gano kwayoyin cutar da aka samar a martani ga kamuwa da cutar.
Ana tabbatar da kwayar cutar a cikin samfura ta hanyar RT-PCR, wanda ke gano RNA na coronavirus.
Wannan gwajin takamaiman ne kuma an tsara shi ne don gano SARS-CoV-2 RNA kawai.
Ana amfani da shi don tabbatar da kamuwa da cuta na kwanan nan ko kuma na aiki.
Ana iya amfani da gano ƙwayoyin cuta (serology) don ganewar asali da kuma lura da yawan jama'a.
Gwajin rigakafin yana nuna yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar, har da waɗanda alamun cutar ba su da tsanani da za a iya sanar da su ko kuma waɗanda ba su da alamun cutar.
Za a iya ƙayyade ainihin yawan mutuwar cutar da matakin rigakafin garken a cikin jama'a daga sakamakon wannan gwajin.
Saboda iyakancewar gwaji, a watan Maris na shekarar 2020 babu wata ƙasa da ke da tabbataccen bayanai game da yaduwar cutar a cikin al'ummarta.
A ranar 23 ga Maris, babu wata ƙasa da ta gwada fiye da kashi 3 cikin ɗari na yawan jama'arta, kuma akwai bambancin da ke tsakanin adadin gwajin da aka yi a ƙasashe.
Wannan canji yana iya shafar yawan mutuwar da ake samu, wanda a wasu ƙasashe za a iya ƙaruwa sosai.
Ta amfani da halayen polymerase chain reaction tare da jujjuyawar lokaci (rRT-PCR), ana iya yin gwajin a kan samfuran numfashi da aka samu ta hanyoyi daban-daban, gami da shafa hanci ko samfurin hawaye.
Sakamakon yana zuwa cikin sa'o'i kaɗan ko kuma kwanaki biyu.
Gwajin RT-PCR da aka yi tare da shafawa a cikin farjin ne kawai za a iya dogara da shi a cikin makon farko na cutar.
Daga baya, kwayar cutar za ta iya ɓacewa a cikin makogwaro yayin da take ci gaba da yawaita a cikin huhu.
Ga mutanen da suka kamu da cutar da aka gwada a mako na biyu, a matsayin madadin, za a iya cire kayan samfurin daga cikin hanyoyin numfashi ta hanyar tsotsa ko kuma za a iya amfani da kayan da aka fitar ta hanyar tsinkaye (saki).
An fara gwajin PCR na farko a Charité, Berlin, a watan Janairun 2020 ta amfani da halayen sarkar polymerase tare da jujjuyawar lokaci na ainihi (rRT-PCR), kuma yana aiki a matsayin tushe don kayan aiki 250,000 don rarraba ta Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO).
Birtaniya ta kuma samar da gwaji a ranar 23 ga Janairu, 2020. Kamfanin Kogenebiotech na Koriya ta Kudu ya samar da irin asibiti, kayan aikin gano SARS-CoV-2 bisa PCR (PowerCheck Coronavirus) a ranar 28 ga Janairu, 2020.
Yana neman kwayar "E" da aka raba ta duk kwayar cutar beta, da kuma kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta musamman, RdRp. A China, kungiyar BGI ta kasance ɗaya daga cikin kamfanoni na farko da suka sami amincewar amfani da gaggawa daga Hukumar Kula da Samfuran Kiwon Lafiya ta China don kayan aikin gano SARS-CoV-2 na PCR. A Amurka, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin (CDC) tana rarraba sabon tsarin bincike na Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) na RT-PCR na lokaci-lokaci ga dakunan gwaje-gwajen kiwon lafiyar jama'a ta hanyar Reagent Resource International.
Daya daga cikin gwaje-gwaje guda uku na kwayoyin halitta a cikin tsofaffin sigar kayan gwajin ya haifar da gwajin da ba shi da tabbas dangane da abubuwan da suka lalace da kuma matsalar gwaji a CDC a Atlanta; wannan ya haifar da matsakaita na ƙasa da samfura 100 a rana ana aiwatar da su cikin nasara a cikin watan Fabrairu na 2020.
Ba a yi la'akari da gwajin da ke amfani da bangarori biyu ba har zuwa 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma daga nan sai an ba da izinin gida da na jihar don fara gwajin.
Hukumar Abinci da Magunguna ta amince da gwajin a karkashin izinin amfani da gaggawa.
Daga 5 ga Maris, 2020, LabCorp ta sanar da samuwar gwajin COVID-19 na kasa bisa RT-PCR.
Quest Diagnostics kuma ta samar da gwajin COVID-19 a duk ƙasar daga 9 ga Maris, 2020.
Babu wani takunkumi na yawa da aka sanar; dole ne a yi tattara da sarrafa samfurori bisa ga bukatun CDC.
A Rasha, Cibiyar Bincike ta Jiha a kan Kwayoyin cuta da Fasaha ta Halitta, VECTOR ce ta tsara kuma ta samar da gwajin COVID-19.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, an yi rajistar gwajin ta Hukumar Kula da Lafiya ta Tarayya. A ranar 12 ga Maris, 2020, Mayo Clinic ta yi ikirarin cewa ta kirkiro gwajin da zai iya gano cutar COVID-19. A ranar 13 ga Maris, 2020, Roche Diagnostics ta sami amincewar FDA don gwajin da za a iya gudanarwa cikin awanni 3.5 a kan sikelin, don haka ta ba da damar injin guda ɗaya ya aiwatar da kimanin gwaje-gwaje 4,128 a cikin awanni 24.
A ranar 19 ga Maris, 2020, FDA ta ba da izinin Amfani da Gaggawa (Amurka) ga Abbott Labs don gwaji a cikin tsarin m2000 na Abbott; FDA ta ba da izini ga Hologic, LabCorp, da Thermo Fisher Scientific.
A ranar 21 ga Maris, 2020, Cepheid ya kuma sami US daga FDA don gwajin da ke ɗaukar kimanin minti 45.
Hukumar FDA ta amince da gwajin da ke amfani da fasahar isothermic nucleic acid amplification maimakon PCR.
Tun da ba ya bukatar jerin juzu'i na zafin jiki, wannan hanyar za ta iya samar da sakamako mai kyau a cikin minti biyar kawai da kuma sakamako mara kyau a cikin minti 13.
A halin yanzu akwai kimanin na'urori 18,000 a Amurka kuma Abbott na fatan kara samarwa don samar da gwaje-gwaje 50,000 a kowace rana. Ana samar da gwajin da ke amfani da kwayar cutar monoclonal kuma ta danganta shi musamman ga furotin nucleocapsid (N) na sabon kwayar cutar korona a Taiwan, tare da tsammanin samar da sakamako cikin mintuna 15 zuwa 20 kamar yadda gwajin hanzari na mura yake.
Wani bita na wallafe-wallafen a watan Maris na shekarar 2020 ya kammala da cewa "hotunan kirji suna da ƙarancin ƙimar bincike a farkon matakan, yayin da CT, CT scan, na iya kasancewa a gaban bayyanar cututtuka".
Halaye na yau da kullun a cikin CT sun haɗa da ƙarancin gilashin gilashi mai yawa tare da rarraba baya, gefen, da kuma asymmetric.
Ƙarfin ƙwayar cuta, da kuma ƙullawa suna canjawa yayin da cutar take ci gaba.
Wani bincike da ya kwatanta PCR da CT a Wuhan a wurin da cutar ta bulla ya nuna cewa CT ya fi PCR saukin kamuwa da cutar, ko da yake ba ta da takamaiman bayani, kuma yawancin abubuwan da ke cikin hoton sun yi daidai da wasu cututtukan huhu da kuma hanyoyin cutar.
Tun daga Maris 2020, Kwalejin Kula da Radiology ta Amurka ta ba da shawarar cewa "Kada a yi amfani da CT don yin bincike ko a matsayin gwajin farko don gano COVID-19". Tun daga Maris 2020, CDC ta ba da shawarar PCR don dubawa na farko.
Wani ɓangare na amsawar garkuwar jiki ga kamuwa da cuta shi ne samar da ƙwayoyin cuta ciki har da IgM da IgG.
Ana iya amfani da su wajen gano kamuwa da cuta a cikin mutane da suka fara kamuwa da cuta kwanaki 7 ko kuma jim kadan bayan bayyanar cututtuka, domin tantance rigakafi, da kuma wajen lura da al'umma. Ana iya yin gwajin a cibiyar gwaje-gwaje (CLT) ko ta hanyar gwajin gwaje-gwaje na nesa (PoCT).
Tsarin sarrafa kansa mai inganci a yawancin dakunan gwaje-gwaje na asibiti zai iya yin waɗannan gwaje-gwajen, amma samuwarsu zai dogara ne akan yawan samar da kowane tsarin.
Don CLT, ana amfani da samfurin jini guda ɗaya, ko da yake ana iya amfani da samfurori da yawa don biye da amsawar rigakafi.
Don PoCT, ana samun samfurin jini guda ɗaya ta hanyar sutura.
Ba kamar hanyoyin PCR ba, ba a buƙatar matakin tattarawa kafin gwaji. A ranar 26 ga Maris, 2020, FDA ta nuna ƙungiyoyi 29 da suka sanar da hukumar kamar yadda ake buƙata, kuma daga yanzu sun cancanci rarraba gwajin rigakafin su.
Ya zuwa ranar 7 ga Afrilu, 2020, FDA ta amince da gwajin guda ɗaya kawai tare da izinin amfani da gaggawa. A ƙarshen Maris, 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics da Epitope Diagnostics sun sami amincewar Turai don kayan gwajin su, waɗanda zasu iya gano IgG da IgA antibodies ga kwayar cutar a cikin samfuran jini.
Ana iya gwada ɗarurruwan samfurori a cikin sa'o'i kaɗan, kuma hakan yana da sauri fiye da gwajin PCR na RNA na ƙwayoyin cuta.
Antibodies yawanci ana gano su ne kwanaki 14 bayan fara kamuwa da cutar. A farkon watan Afrilu, Burtaniya ta ga cewa babu wani daga cikin kayan gwajin antibody da aka saya da ya isa a yi amfani da su.
Hong Kong ta shirya tsarin da marasa lafiya masu zargi za su iya zama a gida, "sashen gaggawa zai ba mai haƙuri bututun samfurin", dole ne su fitar da saliva a cikin bututun, su aika shi kuma su sami sakamako bayan ɗan lokaci. NHS na Burtaniya ta sanar da cewa tana daidaita tsarin don gwada masu zargi a gida, wanda ke kawar da haɗarin mai haƙuri ya cutar da wasu idan sun je asibiti ko buƙatar kashe motar asibiti idan an yi amfani da ita. A cikin gwajin tuki-ta hanyar COVID-19 a cikin masu zargi, ƙwararren likita yana ɗaukar samfuran lafiya yana ɗaukar matakan kariya.
