OSHA ta ɗauki wasu ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da ma'aikatan gawa a matsayin waɗanda ke cikin manyan ko kuma manyan haɗarin haɗari.
Ayyuka masu haɗarin haɗari sun haɗa da masu isar da magunguna, masu kula da lafiya, ma'aikatan dakin gwaje-gwaje da masu jigilar likitoci, waɗanda ke fuskantar marasa lafiya da aka tabbatar ko ake zargin suna da COVID-19.
Haɗarin fallasa yana da girma sosai idan ma'aikata suka yi hanyoyin samar da aerosol a kan marasa lafiya da aka tabbatar ko ake zargi da COVID-19, ko kuma tattara ko kuma kula da samfuran waɗannan marasa lafiya.
Hanyoyin samar da aerosol sun hada da intubation, hanyoyin haifar da tari, bronchoscopy, wasu hanyoyin da binciken hakori ko tarin kwayoyin cuta.
Ayyuka a cikin ɗakunan gawayi masu haɗari sun haɗa da ma'aikata da ke cikin shirya gawawwakin mutanen da ke da COVID-19 da aka tabbatar ko kuma ana zargin cutar a lokacin mutuwarsu; haɗarin haɗari ya zama mai girma idan sun gudanar da autopsy. Ƙarin sarrafa injiniya don waɗannan rukunin haɗarin sun haɗa da ɗakunan keɓewa don marasa lafiya tare da COVID-19 da aka tabbatar ko kuma ana zargin cutar, gami da lokacin da ake gudanar da hanyoyin samar da iska.
Ƙwararrun iska mai ƙarancin matsin lamba na iya zama mai dacewa a wasu yanayin jana'iza da kuma a fannin kiwon lafiya.
Dole ne a kula da samfurori tare da matakin tsaro na 3 na biosafety.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da shawarar cewa a ware marasa lafiya da ke shiga asibiti a yankuna daban-daban na jira dangane da ko suna da cutar COVID-19. Baya ga wasu EPIs, OSHA ta ba da shawarar masu aikin numfashi don masu aiki a nesa da ƙafa 6 daga marasa lafiya da aka tabbatar ko ake zargin suna da cutar SARS-CoV-2, da kuma masu aikin samar da iska.
A Amurka, NIOSH-yarda N95 masu tace numfashi na fuska ko masu inganci masu inganci dole ne a yi amfani da su a cikin yanayin ingantaccen tsarin kariya na numfashi wanda ya hada da gwajin daidaitawa, horo da kuma binciken likita.
Wasu nau'ikan na'urorin numfashi na iya samar da kariya da kuma inganta kwanciyar hankali ga ma'aikaci. WHO ba ta ba da shawarar yin amfani da riguna ba, tun da COVID-19 cuta ce ta numfashi, kuma ba a watsa ta ta ruwa na jiki ba.
WHO ta ba da shawarar sanya abin rufe fuska na tiyata kawai ga ma'aikatan tantancewa a wurin shiga.
Ga masu sana'a da ke tattara samfurin numfashi, kula ko jigilar marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19 ba tare da hanyoyin samar da iska ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar sanya abin rufe fuska, tabarau na kariya ko kariya ta fuska, suturar tiyata da safofin hannu.
Idan an yi aikin samar da aerosol, sai a maye gurbin abin rufe fuska da na N95 ko FFP2.
Tunda wadatar EPIs a duniya ba ta isa ba, WHO ta ba da shawarar rage buƙatar EPIs ta hanyar telemedicine, shinge na zahiri kamar windows masu haske, ba da damar waɗanda ke cikin kulawar kai tsaye ga marasa lafiya su shiga ɗaki tare da mai cutar COVID-19, ta amfani da EPI kawai da ake buƙata don takamaiman aikin, ci gaba da amfani da na'urar numfashi ɗaya ba tare da cire shi ba yayin kula da marasa lafiya da yawa tare da ganewar asali iri ɗaya, saka idanu da daidaita sarkar samar da EPI, da hana amfani da abin rufe fuska ta mutanen da ba su da alamun cutar.
