Enzyme mai canza angiotensin nau'in 2 (ECA2) enzyme ne wanda ke haɗuwa da farfajiyar waje (mambran sel) na ƙwayoyin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ECA2 yana kawar da aikin enzyme mai canza angiotensin (ECA) ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin II da kuma kara Ang (1-7), yana mai da shi magani mai alkawari da aka yi niyya don magance cututtukan zuciya. ECA2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin hanyar shiga cikin ƙwayoyin cuta ga wasu ƙwayoyin cuta.
An kira kwayar halitta ta mutum hECA2.
Enzyme mai canza angiotensin nau'in 2 shine zinc-containing metallosome wanda ke cikin farfajiyar endothelial da sauran ƙwayoyin halitta.
Kwayar ECA2 tana dauke da wani yanki na peptidase M2 mai N-terminal da kuma wani yanki na C-terminal wanda ke dauke da amino acid da colectrin a cikin tsarin koda.
ECA2 shine mai wucewa guda ɗaya na nau'in 1 membrane protein, tare da yankin da ke aiki da enzymatically wanda aka fallasa a farfajiyar ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu da sauran kayan.
Ana cire yankin ECA2 na waje da kwayar halitta daga yankin transmembrane ta wani enzyme da ake kira sheddase, kuma an saki furotin mai narkewa a cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe a fitar da shi cikin fitsari.
ECA2 tana cikin gabobin jiki da yawa: ECA2 tana da alaƙa da membrane na manyan ƙwayoyin alveolar na huhu na nau'in II, ƙwayoyin enterocytes na ƙananan hanji, ƙwayoyin endothelial na arterial da na venous, da ƙwayoyin tsoka na arterial a yawancin gabobin jiki.
An kuma sami bayyanawar ECA2 a cikin kwakwalwar kwakwalwa, cortex striatum, hypothalamus, da kuma kwakwalwar kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ECA2 shi ne ya zama mai daidaitawa ga ECA.
ECA tana cire hormone na angiotensin na nau'i na I zuwa angiotensin na nau'i na II wanda ke haifar da hawan jini.
ECA2 a bayansa yana cire phenylalanine na amino acid mai amfani da carboxymal daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana ruwa a cikin angiotensin mai yaduwa (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-Gist-Pro-OH).
ECA2 kuma yana ƙyamar wasu peptide da yawa, gami da [des-Arg9]-bradicinine, apilin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
ECA2 kuma tana daidaita jigilar membrane na mai ɗaukar amino acid mai tsaka tsaki SLC6A19 kuma an haɗa shi da cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin mai wucewa, ECA2 yana aiki a matsayin babban wurin shigarwa cikin ƙwayoyin cuta ga wasu ƙwayoyin cuta na coronaviruses, ciki har da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (ƙwayoyin cuta da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (ƙwayoyin cuta da ke haifar da COVID-19).
