Rigakafin ya ƙunshi lambar kwayar halitta mara lahani da aka kwafa daga kwayar cutar da ke haifar da cutar. An nuna haɓaka mai dogara da ƙwayoyin cuta a matsayin ƙalubale mai yuwuwa don haɓaka allurar rigakafin SARS-CoV-2, amma wannan yana da rikici.
Akwai gwaje-gwaje sama da 300 da ake yi tun daga watan Afrilu na shekarar 2020.
Gwaje-gwaje bakwai sun gwada maganin da aka amince da shi na zazzabin cizon sauro, ciki har da gwaje-gwaje huɗu da suka yi amfani da hydroxychloroquine ko chloroquine.
Sake tura magungunan rigakafin cutar ya ƙunshi yawancin binciken kasar Sin, tare da gwajin asibiti tara na Phase III na remdesivir a kasashe daban-daban saboda rahoton karshen watan Afrilu.
Ana gudanar da bincike mai ƙarfi game da ci gaban magungunan magani da allurar rigakafi don COVID-19 a watan Afrilu na 2020. Ana kimanta magungunan rigakafin cutar da ke akwai don maganin COVID-19, gami da remdesivir, chloroquine da hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir da lopinavir/ritonavir haɗe tare da interferon beta.
An yi ƙoƙari don tabbatar da tasirin remdesivir tun daga Maris 2020.
An ga ci gaba a asibiti a cikin marasa lafiya da aka yi amfani da remdesivir ta hanyar tausayi.
Ana gudanar da gwajin asibiti na mataki na uku a Amurka, China da Italiya. An yi nazarin maganin chloroquine a China a watan Fabrairun 2020 tare da sakamakon farko.
Duk da haka, akwai buƙatun sake duba binciken tare.
Hukumomin kiwon lafiya na Koriya da na Sin sun ba da shawarar yin amfani da maganin chloroquine.
Koyaya, Cibiyar Virology ta Wuhan, yayin da take ba da shawarar kashi ɗaya na gram kowace rana, ta yi gargadin cewa ninki biyu na wannan adadin yana da haɗari sosai kuma yana iya zama mai kisa.
A ranar 28 ga Maris, 2020, FDA ta ba da izinin amfani da gaggawa na hydroxychloroquine da chloroquine a kan shawarar likitoci da ke kula da mutane da COVID-19. Na 7 na jagororin Sin kuma ya haɗa da interferon, ribavirin ko umifenovir don amfani da su kan COVID-19.
Bayanai na farko sun nuna cewa ana buƙatar manyan allurai na ribavirin don hana SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
An ba da shawarar yin ƙarin nazarin nitazoxanide a cikin in vivo bayan ya nuna ƙarancin ƙwayar SARS-CoV-2. Nazarin ya nuna cewa furotin na farko na farawa a cikin shiri ta hanyar protease na serine 2 (TMPRSS2) yana da mahimmanci ga shigar SARS-CoV-2 ta hanyar hulɗa tare da mai karɓar ACE2.
Nazarin kan chloroquine da hydroxychloroquine tare da ko ba tare da azithromycin ba suna da manyan iyakoki waɗanda suka hana ƙungiyar likitanci ɗaukar waɗannan magunguna ba tare da ƙarin bincike ba. Oseltamivir baya hana SARS-CoV-2 in vitro kuma ba shi da wani aiki da aka sani a cikin maganin COVID-19.
Cytokine storm na iya zama rikitarwa a cikin matakan ƙarshe na COVID-19 mai tsanani.
Akwai shaidar cewa hydroxychloroquine na iya samun kaddarorin anti-cytokine. Tocilzumab an sanya shi cikin jagororin magani ta Hukumar Lafiya ta China bayan kammala karamin binciken.
Ana ci gaba da gwajin gwaji na kashi na 2 a Italiya bayan da ya nuna sakamako mai kyau a cikin mutane masu ciwon mai tsanani.
Idan aka haɗa shi da gwajin jini na ferritin na jini don gano guguwar cytokine, ana sa ran zai kawar da waɗannan ci gaban, waɗanda ake ganin su ne suka sa wasu da suka kamu da cutar suka mutu.
An amince da mai adawa da mai karɓar interleukin-6 ta FDA bisa ga nazarin yanayin baya game da maganin cutar cutar cytokine mai hana yaduwar steroid ta hanyar wani dalili daban, maganin CAR T cell a cikin 2017.
Har zuwa yanzu babu wani tabbataccen, sarrafawa da aka tsara wanda ya nuna cewa tocilzumab magani ne mai inganci ga CRS.
Ana binciken canja wurin tsarkakewa da kuma ƙwayoyin cuta da aka ƙera da tsarin garkuwar jiki na waɗanda suka warke daga COVID-19 zuwa mutanen da suke bukatarsu a matsayin hanyar da ba rigakafi ba na rigakafin da ba na aiki.
An gwada wannan dabarar a SARS, amma ba ta ba da tabbaci ba.
Rashin tasirin kwayar cuta shine tsarin aikin da ake tsammani wanda maganin rigakafin rigakafi na iya haifar da kariya daga SARS-CoV-2.
Sauran hanyoyin, kamar su antibody-dependent cytotoxicity da/ko phagocytosis, na iya yiwuwa.
Ana kuma ci gaba da yin wasu hanyoyin maganin ƙwayoyin cuta, kamar yin amfani da ƙwayoyin cuta na monoclonal da aka yi.
Za a iya ƙara samar da maganin warkarwa, wanda ya ƙunshi ruwan jini daga marasa lafiya da suka warke kuma ya ƙunshi ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman ga wannan cuta, don saurin aiwatarwa.
